data.description: Don't miss this big, beautiful home in the desirable Southern Dunes. 6 large bedrooms, 5 full bathrooms, huge finished basement with kitchenette, bedroom, bathroom, storage room and enormous rec room. Main floor has 1 bedroom and full bath. Upper level is where there are 4 more large bedrooms and 3 more full bathrooms. Home is virtually maintenance free with stone and cement board siding and sits on quiet street with 6' tall privacy fence, 3 car attached garage partially converted to a climate controlled salon. This home is made for a large family. At less than $89 per square foot, this house won't last long.
